BottleCollector

This is a simple 2D game demo.

The game uses the libgdx multi platform graphics library.

The project contains subprojects for Android, Desktop and GWT. Only the Android version is currently tested.

Explained in my german book "Spieleprogrammierung mit Android Studio":

https://www.rheinwerk-verlag.de/spieleprogrammierung-mit-android-studio_3537/